; https://github.com/tldr-pages/tldr/blob/master/pages/common/ppmmix.md

% ppmmix, common

# Blend the specified PPM images using fadefactor to control the weight of each image
ppmmix <fadefactor> {{path/to/input_file1.ppm path/to/input_file2.ppm ...}} > <path_to_output_file_ppm>
